projects:
[{'title': 'Education Board Result Publication System', 'date': {'start': {'month': 8, 'day': None, 'year': 2016}, 'end': {'month': 8, 'day': None, 'year': 2016}}, 'description': 'This project serves Public Exam Results of Bangladesh covering JSC, SSC, HSC under Education Boards of Bangladesh. Due to the nature of public access it has been designed to serve results quickly using cutting edge technologies. We believe that this project is helpful for the general public to get results instantly. This is the first project that shows detailed marks sheets after result is published (subject to the consent by respective Boards). It has a real-time access statistics that shows result access counts in real time.
Features:
Individual Result (Detailed Result of individual candidate)
Institution Result (Result of individual Institutions)
Center Result (Result of individual Exam Centres)
District Result (Result of individual Districts/Zillas)
Institution Analytics (Graphical Analytics for individual Institutions)
Board Analytics (Graphical Analytics for individual Boards)

Homepage: https://eboardresults.com/
App URL: https://eboardresults.com/app/', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'AYUB', 'last_name': 'ALI', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Founder @ Nixtec Systems'}]}, {'title': "Teachers' Recruitment Service  for NTRCA", 'date': {'start': {'month': 4, 'day': None, 'year': 2016}, 'end': {'month': 4, 'day': None, 'year': 2016}}, 'description': "This service recruits teachers for institutions under NTRCA (Non-Govt. Teachers' Registration and Certification Authority). Under public circular of NTRCA for teacher recruitment, all Non-Govt. educational institutions provide their requisitions online. Based on the requisitions eligible candidates (NTRCA certificate holders) apply to their desired institutions. At last result is processed and published online based on  Combined National Merit and Candidate's choice. The whole steps are done online. In the last recruitment (Cycle 3, 2021) we received requisitions for 54K vacant posts and 9M valid (paid) applications (10M total). Nixtec Systems provided technical Engineering and Development services.", 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'AYUB', 'last_name': 'ALI', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Founder @ Nixtec Systems'}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Bhaktear Uddin', 'headline': None}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Abdul Kader', 'headline': None}]}, {'title': 'SIM Tracking System for Teletalk Bangladesh Limited', 'date': {'start': {'month': 1, 'day': None, 'year': 2015}, 'end': {'month': 1, 'day': None, 'year': 2015}}, 'description': "SIM Tracking System is a Mobile Core Network Solution. It resolves location of a mobile subscriber from HLR/VLR and shows it over map or API response. Given a MSISDN it sends query to HLR (through MSC, over SIGTRAN/IP) to get Subscriber's Location. HLR in turns consults corresponding VLR to find the location. This process is done without the user making any events (SMS/Call/etc.). Developed in C. The Project URL is the front-end to translate the received LAC/CI (from HLR) to Lat-Long to map on Google Map.

Implemented SS7 Stack (M3UA, SCCP, TCAP, MAP) to communicate with MSC/HLR.
Can be used for Location Based Services.", 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'AYUB', 'last_name': 'ALI', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Founder @ Nixtec Systems'}]}, {'title': 'USSD Gateway and Platform for Mobile Financial Service and integration with existing VAS Services (for Teletalk Bangladesh Ltd.)', 'date': {'start': {'month': 7, 'day': None, 'year': 2014}, 'end': {'month': 7, 'day': None, 'year': 2014}}, 'description': 'USSD Gateway provides interactive services for Mobile Subscribers. The USSD Gateway communicates to the Core Network using SS7 protocols. This project implemented M3UA, SCCP, TCAP, MAP layers and communicates over SCTP. It was written in C. It has both MO and MT support. It communicates with a backend API system written in PHP and using MySQL database. School Admission System', 'date': {'start': {'month': 11, 'day': None, 'year': 2015}, 'end': {'month': 11, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': 'This project takes requisitions from Govt. institutions for classes 1-9. Candidates would apply based on the requisition to their institutions of interest. After that they would get Admit Cards. The admit cards would be used to appear for exam. After exams institutions would upload marks and system would generate result in real-time.
